---
title: Chicken & Creamy Chive Sauce with Oven-Baked Potato Chips & Garlic Greens
description: With their delicate onion flavour and vibrant colour, chives make a sauce sing! This creamy chive sauce on seared chicken breast is packed with flavour, and with baked potato chips and garlicky veggies on the side, it makes a meal everyone will love.
